node.text: We wear the Cat badge with honour. We engineer every phone to provide ultimate reliability and guarantee no down time on the toughest of jobs; because when it is Cat, it just works.

Don’t just settle for a splash proof phone. We design our phones to be used in the toughest environments, so you can use them with confidence in the most extreme conditions and know they’ll always survive a fall into water.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on July 05, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: The Cat B40 is an industrial strength, professional grade, 4G feature phone with an added silver ion based anti-microbial additive. Waterproof, drop proof and dust proof, the Cat B40 gives confidence under pressure with exceptional germ defence.

node.text: Heading out on the water this weekend? All of our rugged smartphones, including the Cat S62 Pro, are fully waterproof to a depth of 1.5 metres so you can make a splash worry free!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on May 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'FLIR'.

node.text: We love seeing how you use your @FLIR camera in your Cat phone to capture details you can't see with the naked eye. Share your pictures with us using #CatFLIR

node.text: The Cat S42 H+ blends a rugged phone with antimicrobial silver ions. Making it the perfect choice whether you work in a hygienic conscious environment or in the harshest of conditions. The S42 H+ is the perfect companion.

node.text:
We have taken the reliable and rugged body of the Cat® S42 and have enhanced it with antibacterial silver ions. Creating our first phone that is not only rugged as hell but provides extreme hygiene protection. 

Discover more about the Cat® S42 H+ through the link in our bio

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on April 13, 2021. May be a closeup of one or more people and phone.

node.text: The Cat®  S62 Pro has a modern, rugged design and is protected by a high grade aluminium body, and the latest toughened scratch-resistant Corning® Gorilla® Glass 6.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on April 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
This World Health Day we at Cat® Phones want to say thank you to all of the frontline workers that work tirelessly to help us in our hours of need. 

#WorldHealthDay #globalhealth

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on April 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, screen and phone.

node.text: Don’t compromise when it comes to being clean. The Cat® S52 can be washed time and time again, in warm water, bleach and hand sanitizer.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CatRuggedPhones on March 31, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, body of water and indoor.

node.text:
Work hard, clean easy with Cat® phones. So tough you can wash it whenever you wash your hands, no matter how often.

#TheToughChoice #EasyClean #hygiene #WhenSmartMeansClean #Catruggedphones
